  <p><anchor n="T.50.2062.0910c03"/><lb ed="T" n="0910c03"/><persName key="A008281">釋居敬</persName>字<persName key="A008281">心淵</persName>別號<persName key="A008281">蘭雪</persName>。學通內外善屬文<lb ed="T" n="0910c04"/>精嚴律部。禮金陵<placeName key="PL000000008822">大報恩寺</placeName><persName key="A012732">一雨</persName>和尚職<lb ed="T" n="0910c05"/>知客。後參杭州<placeName key="PL000000011638">集慶寺</placeName><persName key="A008283">東源法師</persName>。於懺摩<lb ed="T" n="0910c06"/>堂居第一座。從而講周易<!--經名ID -->。<date from-iso="1403" key="j22335262235534" to-iso="1408">永樂初</date>奉。<lb ed="T" n="0910c07"/>詔校大藏經<!--經名ID -->預修會典。已而住持上海<placeName key="PL000000008381">廣<lb ed="T" n="0910c08"/>福講寺</placeName>。遷松江<placeName key="PL000000008462">普照</placeName>大開法席一十三載。<lb ed="T" n="0910c09"/>建<placeName key="PL000000057335">大雄殿</placeName><placeName key="PL000000057333">海月堂</placeName><placeName key="PL000000057334">三解脫門</placeName>。廊廡重軒精舍<lb ed="T" n="0910c10"/>香積煥然新之。七眾瞻仰道風大扇。</p>
